{"Id":480217,"Title":"言志赠友人","Dynasty":"明","Author":"刘崧","Context":"深山邃谷，虎豹所凭。玄雾翳云，蛟龙斯升。芸芸暮蜉，缉缉秋蝇。嘅彼下士，志何由兴。岁年云徂，冰雪侵凌。眷彼皓首，含涕抚膺。契予夙好，嘉尔友朋。亦有旨酒，如溜如渑。可以乐衎，高融咸登。仰睇白日，翩其相仍。道谊罔敦，忧患式增。不曰尼父，饮水曲肱。媚货附桓，圣人不能。我行东原，以陟崚嶒。言采荣木，手挽其藤。素秋以风，霜露乃凝。黄鹄斯举，天高气澄。送子于迈，服子徽称。理棹河湄，赪霞晨蒸。何以益我，敦教而承。友道之薄，噫其春冰。尔弘其居，夕惕兢兢。人亦有言，谷增而陵。圣途云遐，气力曷胜。勖尔踯躅，暨于鶱腾。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"6d8260027c6fc639c21e9992c7225b95","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6366110,"Sentence":"不曰尼父，饮水曲肱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bú yuē nǐ fǔ ，yin shui qū gōng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":11,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366111,"Sentence":"媚货附桓，圣人不能。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mèi huò fù huán ，shèng rén bú néng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366112,"Sentence":"我行东原，以陟崚嶒。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ háng dōng yuán ，yi zhì lǐng céng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":13,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366113,"Sentence":"言采荣木，手挽其藤。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yán cǎi róng mù ，shǒu wǎn jī téng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":14,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366114,"Sentence":"素秋以风，霜露乃凝。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sù qīu yi fēng ，shuāng lòu nǎi nǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":15,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366115,"Sentence":"黄鹄斯举，天高气澄。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huáng gǔ sī jǔ ，tiān gāo qì chéng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366116,"Sentence":"送子于迈，服子徽称。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"sòng zi yú mài ，fú zi huī chèn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366099,"Sentence":"深山邃谷，虎豹所凭。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shēn shān suì gǔ ，hū bào suǒ pǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6366100,"Sentence":"玄雾翳云，蛟龙斯升。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xuán wù yì yún ，jiāo lón